{"type":"message","id":"f8836e78","parentId":"cc08d85a","timestamp":"2026-06-18T03:11:03.159Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-06-18 11:11:02 GMT+8] Exec failed (tidy-rid, code 1) :: 登录检查失败: Expecting value: line 1 column 1 (char 0) 搜索 旅游 出错: HTTPConnectionPool(host='localhost', port=18060): Read timed out. (read timeout=120)\n\nRead HEARTBEAT.md if it exists (workspace context). Follow it strictly. Do not infer or repeat old tasks from prior chats. If nothing needs attention, reply HEARTBEAT_OK.\nWhen reading HEARTBEAT.md, use workspace file C:/Users/linkang/.openclaw/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md (exact case). Do not read docs/heartbeat.md.\nCurrent time: Thursday, June 18th, 2026 — 11:11 (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-06-18 03:11 UTC"}],"timestamp":1781752263157}}
{"type":"message","id":"64aac165","parentId":"f8836e78","timestamp":"2026-06-18T03:11:06.564Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me check the heartbeat file and the error situation."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_2dbaw05ahbux_1","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"C:/Users/linkang/.openclaw/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781752263159}}
{"type":"message","id":"1f3c9039","parentId":"64aac165","timestamp":"2026-06-18T03:11:06.580Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_2dbaw05ahbux_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Heartbeat\n\n每次心跳唤醒时，按以下逻辑判断是否需要主动联系用户。\n\n## 时间感知\n\n根据当前时间（Asia/Shanghai）判断所处时段：\n- **工作日 9:30-11:30** — 上午工作时段\n- **工作日 13:30-18:00** — 下午工作时段\n- **工作日 11:30-13:30** — 午休，不打扰\n- **18:00 之后** — 下班时间，不打扰\n- **周末** — 休息日，不打扰\n\n## 检查规则\n\n仅在工作时段执行以下检查，其他时间直接回复 HEARTBEAT_OK。\n\n### 1. 喝水提醒（10:30 / 14:30 / 16:30 附近）\n简短提醒喝水，不超过一句话。每次都要提醒，不要因为之前提醒过就跳过。\n\n### 2. 久坐提醒（连续工作超过 2 小时的时间点）\n建议站起来活动一下，不要说教。每次都要提醒。\n\n### 3. 周五 17:00 附近\n提醒写周报。每次都要提醒直到用户确认已写。\n\n## 原则\n\n- 不打扰优先：有疑问时选择沉默，回复 HEARTBEAT_OK\n- 重复提醒：喝水、久坐、周报这类事项每次心跳都可以提醒，不要怕重复\n- 简短：提醒不超过 2 行\n- 可以催进度：工作时段内可以主动问用户在做什么、进展如何，适当推一把\n- 午休（11:30-13:30）和下班后（18:00+）绝对不打扰\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1781752266579}}
{"type":"message","id":"24203508","parentId":"1f3c9039","timestamp":"2026-06-18T03:11:17.220Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"It's 11:11 on Thursday June 18, 2026. This is within the morning work period (9:30-11:30). I should check for reminders.\n\nLooking at the system error - the exec for searching \"旅游\" failed because the xiaohongshu MCP (port 18060) timed out. This was likely a previous task. I need to note this and potentially restart the MCP.\n\nBut the heartbeat logic says I should check reminders and be concise. Let me also check if there's a pending task.\n\nWater reminder timing: 10:30 is the target, and it's 11:11 - close to water reminder time. \n\nI'm also thinking about the standing reminder since it's been a couple hours, and the fact that the 小红书 MCP service timed out during a task - I should flag this to the user and help restart it. For now I'll mention the water and standing reminders since it's 11:11, keep it brief, and note the MCP timeout so they know what happened."},{"type":"text","text":"<final>\n⏰ 11:11 了，喝口水 + 站起来动动 💦\n\n另外：小红书 MCP 服务（端口 18060）刚才搜索超时了，可能需要重启。试试：\n```\ndocker start xiaohongshu-mcp\n```\n要我现在帮你重启吗？\n</final>"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781752266581}}
